Although you share more traits with those relatives with whom

00:00:02.860 --> 00:00:05.800
you're most genetically similar, let's say your parents, and your

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:09.060
brothers and sisters, this doesn't mean that your closest relatives

00:00:09.060 --> 00:00:12.980
like your parents or siblings share every trait that you have.

