00:02:07.670 --> 00:02:11.760
square and if they're not lactose intolerant, if they're

00:02:11.760 --> 00:02:15.380
lactose tolerant, right, they can actually digest milk products,

00:02:15.380 --> 00:02:17.010
then we're not going to shade the circle at all.

00:02:17.010 --> 00:02:20.140
We're going to leave it empty. It really is that

00:02:20.140 --> 00:02:22.560
simple. So let's try to build a pedigree for

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:26.720
a particular individual concerning the trait of lactose intolerance.

